		"description": "<p>This infused hair dye appears as a thick paste and can be made in any color. When applied to a creature&rsquo;s hair, it permanently and automatically dyes their hair the corresponding color. This dye never fades or needs to be reapplied, and if a new color of Never-Fade Dye is applied the hair takes on the new color with no traces of the old.</p>\n<p>While the color appears normal and natural to any nonmagical means of detection, it can be detected by spells such as @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.kaye34nheyrit487]{Detect Magic} dispelled by spells such as @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.hms9kdl2qoqjjrs4]{Dispel Magic}.</p>",
